Starting a new Rails project

Create the project with:
rails new project -d postgresql

Creating Models

Models are singular and lowercase unless there is muti words then they are snake case.

Controller are plural located in app/controllers directory
each controller is named by class followed by the word "Controller"

Create the class definition:
  class ClassnameController < ApplicationController
    def index
     @classes= Class.all
    end
  end

  Add the route as a method
